headline.print_headline: Phelps Beaten in First Comeback Final
headline.main: Phelps Beaten in First Comeback Final

lead_paragraph: Michael Phelps suffered a narrow loss to his old rival Ryan Lochte in his comeback to competitive swimming on Thursday, but still showed enough to suggest he will be a force to be reckoned with.
